messages.title: Newark's gridlock is coming to an end
messages.content: Robert's 5-year lobbying ministers and using his influence to persuade Government to secure the investment will be the largest investment. Victory brings the town since the Victorians brought the railways to Newark improving quality of life for everyone and helping to generate jobs and prosperity.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Robert Jenrick has secured a £450 million investment that will see Newark's bypass completed from the A46 to the A1 at Winthorpe. This effort is expected to reduce gridlock in Newark.

housing.content: Securing investment for the largest project since the Victorian era that will bring prosperity and generate jobs.

images.caption: Robert Jenrick standing beside the roadway with the caption 'From Robert Jenrick, your local Conservative candidate' and slogans such as '£450MILLION A46 BYPASS SECURED' and 'GET BREXIT DONE.'
